# Starmernomics Pixel Art Concepts

## 1. Banner

```
+----------------------------------------------------------+
|  STARMERNOMICS                                           |
|  [PM: Starmer-Penfold]   [Royal Marine]                  |
|  Dystopian cityscape, rundown Parliament, papers flying  |
+----------------------------------------------------------+
```

## 2. Logo

```
   _________
  |         |
  | (O) (O) |   <-- PM's glasses (Starmer-Penfold fusion)
  |   ---   |
  |  STAR   |
  | NOMICS  |
  |_________|
```

## 3. Avatar

```
  .---.
 ( o o )   <-- round glasses
  \ ^ /    <-- Starmer's hair
  / _ \
 /|_|_|\   <-- suit and tie
```

## 4. Scene

```
+--------------------------+
| [PM at desk, worried]    |
| [Royal Marine, alert]    |
| Papers, briefcase,       |
| city in background       |
+--------------------------+
```

## 5. Chapter Intro Screen

```
+---------------------+
| CHAPTER 1: THE DEBT |
