```

---

**Color Palette Suggestions:**
- Backgrounds: #5D5B6A (gray), #A67D4F (brown), #B85042 (dark red), #32746D (green)
- Characters: PM suit (navy), glasses (black), Marine uniform (dark green/blue), skin tones (light beige, tan)

---

**Notes:**
- These are starter concepts; detailed pixel art can be made using tools like Aseprite, Piskel, or by commissioning a pixel artist.
- If you want, I can generate higher resolution pixel art using AI tools or guide you to do so.

Let me know if you want refinements, full chapter intros, or want to proceed with full digital assets!
